graph LR
    RHOAI[RHOAI Operator<br/>rhods-operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    RHOAI -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift<br/>1.28+ / 4.14+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    RHOAI -.->|traffic mgmt| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh<br/>Istio 2.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHOAI -.->|serverless| Serverless[OpenShift Serverless<br/>Knative 1.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHOAI -.->|certificates| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>1.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHOAI -->|dependency mgmt| OLM[OLM<br/>Operator Lifecycle Manager<br/>REQUIRED]
    RHOAI -->|monitoring infra| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>0.68.0<br/>BUNDLED]

    %% External Services
    RHOAI -->|image pulls| ImageRegistry[Image Registries<br/>registry.redhat.io, quay.io]

    %% Deployed Components (Managed by operator)
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| KServe[KServe<br/>Model Serving]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Jupyter Notebooks]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Kubeflow/Tekton]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model Metadata]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| Ray[Ray<br/>Distributed Computing]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| TrainingOp[Training Operator<br/>Distributed Training]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>Explainability]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job Queuing]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| Feast[Feast Operator<br/>Feature Store]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| MLflow[MLflow Operator<br/>Experiment Tracking]
    RHOAI -->|deploys/manages| LlamaStack[Llama Stack Operator<br/>LLM Deployment]

    %% Platform Services (Managed by operator)
    RHOAI -->|deploys| Monitoring[Monitoring Service<br/>Prometheus/Alertmanager]
    RHOAI -->|configures| Auth[Auth Service<br/>OAuth/RBAC]
    RHOAI -->|configures| Gateway[Gateway Service<br/>API Gateway]
    RHOAI -->|configures| TrustedCA[TrustedCABundle<br/>Custom CA Injection]

    %% Component Dependencies
    KServe -->|requires| ServiceMesh
    KServe -->|requires| Serverless
    Dashboard -->|integrates| KServe
    Dashboard -->|integrates| Workbenches
    Dashboard -->|integrates| Pipelines
    Pipelines -->|integrates| Workbenches
    ModelRegistry -->|integrates| KServe

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|ConsoleLink| Console[OpenShift Console<br/>UI Integration]
    Monitoring -->|ServiceMonitor| PrometheusOp
    RHOAI -->|ServiceMeshMember| ServiceMesh

    %% Styling
    style RHOAI fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

